<br>
Their hands were joined together as they bowed their heads before those Queens that came to them. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uhippolyte.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Hippolyte</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://hometown.aol.com/queenhippolyte/spinningsword.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Vasilissa</span><br>  Posts: 290<br> <font color=#993300>(4/14/01 5:02:42 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> A gift</span><hr size=1> Hippolyte walked slowely towards the couple, her hand held the hand of her own partner in life, Gabby.  Behind them walked the dark guardian of Themiscrya's forest, Marpe.  Behind the guardian walked a pale white horse.  Upon the white's back, he carried a leather bound pack.  <br>
As Hippolyte neared the couple, her hand slipped gently from Gabby's and she saluted her Amazon athelfi..then respectivly nodded to the Devi.  <br>
&quot;Alysia and Eli, I wish you blessings and a simple gift from Themiscrya.  First, we do hope that the gods and Eli's one god do give you much happiness and joy.  And that your union bring's both of you peace in your hearts.  To no longer search for that that you need to fill the empty space in your heart.&quot; Hipp's hand again took her love's hand.  Gabby smiled at both of them.<br>
&quot;As for the gift,&quot; Hippolyte nodded to Marpe, who lead the white stallion towards the couple.<br>
&quot;This stallion has brought me many stronge foals.  Take him as a gift, that your herd shall grow strong as the ones in Themiscrya.&quot;  As she spoke, Marpe released the leather and brought it to her Queen.  Hippolyte took the leather from Marpe and kneeled before the couple...laying the leather upon the ground and releasing it from it's bonds.  As the leather was pulled gently away, it revealed a goblet of gold, delicatly engraved with ornate designs.  Hippolyte picked it up and held it out to Eli.  <br>
&quot;I once received this goblet from Hephaustus.  He said it was a goblet of light and peace,&quot; She smiled. &quot;I thought you should have it now.  Man of Peace and Light.&quot;  She then gave Eli the goblet. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uhippolyte.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Hippolyte</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://hometown.aol.com/queenhippolyte/spinningsword.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Vasilissa</span><br>  Posts: 291<br> <font color=#993300>(4/14/01 5:09:49 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> the gift</span><hr size=1> The small queen then began to unfold the last bit of leather.  It revealed a golden belt, ornatly tooled and engraved with a pack of small wolves around.  In the middle stood a taller wolf, engraved in greater detail.  Hippolyte picked up the belt and held it before Alysia.  <br>
&quot;Athelfi, I believe it is time for you to wear the great symbol of pride for all the ancient queens of the Amazons.  In the old days, a queen was recognized by the wearing of the golden belt.  I know you have heard of the stories of these belts.  And it is time,&quot;Hipp hands it to Alysia. &quot;for you to be belted... my Queen.&quot; Hipp smirked and winked. &quot;This was crafted by Alcippe, our smithy in Themiscrya.  I know she has taken great time and pride in working on this belt for me to give to you. Wear it with pride, athelfi.&quot;<br>
Hippolyte then picked up the leather and rose from the ground...then saluted them with the clink of her guantlets.  <br>
&quot;May the Gods bless you,&quot; she nodded to Marpe who lead the stallion to the Scynthian stables.  Then she and Gabby walked away from the couple. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uqueenmaytha.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Queen Maytha</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#993300>(4/14/01 10:58:44 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.chickpages.com/rants/xamznqnmayx/images/smallmaytha.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Wishes the Best</span><hr size=1> Maytha walks toward Aly and Eli. She neals down and hands out a box to them. Bows head in honor.<br>
<br>
&quot;I wish the greatest through out your marriage. And Congrats on your marriage.&quot; Maytha says as she raises her hand up, handing them the box.<br>
<br>
In the box, it has jewels all around it, and inside, has 2 rings, for the new husband and wife. To show that there love will be eternal. <p><FONT SIZE="10"><FONT FACE="WingDings">Z</FONT></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ulatraariah.showPublicProfile?language=EN>LaTra Ariah</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=C:\America Online 6.0\download\moonicon.bmp BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#993300>(4/15/01 4:34:28 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> A symbol of growth</span><hr size=1> Ari walked forward and smiled softly.<br>
&quot;I want to wish you both the best. Alysia, since I first started your training, you have grown so much...&quot;<br>
A young Amazon girl walks forward carrying a staff a little more than half Alysia's size. Ari smiles and takes the staff, nodding thanks to the younger Amazon.<br>
&quot;This is the staff you trained with, Aly, when we first started.&quot; She knelt and placed the staff before them. &quot;I want to give this to you as a symbol. So that your marraige can continue to grow throughout the years.&quot; She smiled at Aly, then at Eli, stood and moved back to her place in the seats. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ugenesistiberon.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Genesis Tiberon</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 4<br> <font color=#993300>(4/15/01 5:30:10 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Blessings</span><hr size=1> Genesis moved forward to Eli and Aly, looking to them, a small slight nod. &quot;I give you both my blessings&quot; She had that stern wise look to her eyes and face, she continued..&quot;And I bring no gift, as no amount of gifts could compair to the gift of Love, be safe and well in this..bond..&quot; She looked to Aly..and gave a small smile, ALy &amp; Gen had already spoken on amny things in relation to the marriage, Aly knew where Genesis stood. She turns and walks away. <p><A HREF="http://www.monkeegirl.com/rpg" target=_blank"><IMG SRC="http://www.monkeegirl.com/genesisbanner.jpg" border="0"></A></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showMessage?topicID=118.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showMessage?topicID=123.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.emailToFriend?topicID=116.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a F